                <strong>Ingredientes:</strong>
            </p>
            <br />
            <p class="identDIV">
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2-3 avocados pequenos e maduros (devem estar pretos e macios)
            </p>
            <p class="identDIV">
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2 dentes de alho cru picado
            </p>
            <p class="identDIV">
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 lim&atilde;o tahiti, s&oacute; o suco
